name: The Cobalt Watcher - Holo
description:
_Card #16 - Holographic version
_Base points: 12
Holo versions have same base points as its standard version.

Can a watcher be impartial? As one of the four, the ways of the Cobalt could be considered questionable. Many were the stories from the people of the Black Valley witnessing the deathly "pale brightness".
